*Ghost in the Machine Tour (1981–1982)
*Synchronicity Tour (1983–1984)
*The Police Reunion Tour (2007–2008)

==Band members==
===Final line-up===
*Sting – lead and backing vocals, bass guitar, double bass, keyboards 
*Stewart Copeland – drums, percussion, backing vocals, keyboards 
*Andy Summers – guitars, backing and occasional lead vocals, keyboards 

===Past members===
*Henry Padovani – guitars 

